definitions.definition: An Old World monkey of the genus Papio , having dog-like muzzles and large canine teeth, cheek pouches, a short tail, and naked callosities on the buttocks .

main_definition: An Old World monkey of the genus Papio , having dog-like muzzles and large canine teeth, cheek pouches, a short tail, and naked callosities on the buttocks . [from 13th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( colloquial , derogatory ) A foolish or boorish person.
